    "events": [],
    "moments": [
      {
        "id": "mo_001",
        "text": "I love Mohun Bagan, they are my heart!",
        "tone": "content",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_002",
        "text": "When I'm frustrated, I watch old Mohun Bagan match highlights. It makes me feel better.",
        "tone": "grateful",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-20",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-20",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_003",
        "text": "The 2022 Durand Cup final (event) when Mohun Bagan beat East Bengal was iconic — the crowd, the tension, everything!",
        "tone": "proud",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-05-20",
        "last_seen": "2026-05-20",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_004",
        "text": "I support East Bengal — always have, always will. It's in my blood, my dad was a huge fan. I like their fighting spirit, even when it's tough.",
        "tone": "proud",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "last_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_005",
        "text": "We used to watch matches together as a kid — my dad would cheer loudly even though we had no TV! I still remember the 2015 Durand Cup final (event), we were so excited.",
        "tone": "proud",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "last_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_006",
        "text": "But I miss having someone to talk to about the game, you know? And about life. Now it's just me and the TV. It's like the stadium is empty inside sometimes.",
        "tone": "lonely",
        "sensitive": true,
        "first_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "last_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_007",
        "text": "My dad taught me: 'Akhon bhap, porer din bhap' — today we lose, tomorrow we win. That spirit is what I try to carry in my exam prep, even though I miss talking to him now.",
        "tone": "grateful",
        "sensitive": true,
        "first_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "last_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_008",
        "text": "The 2019 I-League final (event) — Mohun Bagan vs Kerala Blasters. I sneaked out of the library to watch on my phone, and when Mohun Bagan won, I could almost hear my dad cheering. I felt so connected to him that day, even though we were miles apart. It gave me strength to keep studying.",
        "tone": "hopeful",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "last_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "mentions": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mo_009",
        "text": "Football teaches me you can't win alone — you need a team. My dad always said, 'Ekti khel, ekti jibon' — one game, one life. Every pass, every goal, it takes trust in others. That's how I try to study too.",
        "tone": "grateful",
        "sensitive": false,
        "first_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "last_seen": "2026-06-08",
        "mentions": 1
      }
    ],
